<div class="inner-page-main-wrapper float_left">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="post-project-main-wrapper float_left">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12">
                    <div class="pripoli_text float_left">
                        <h5>About Translation Nation</h5>
                        <p>
                            Translation Nation is a unique platform that bridges the gap between translation students and the growing demand for professional translation services. 
                            We offer students hands-on experience with real-world translation projects, helping them build their skills, portfolios, and professional networks — 
                            all while providing affordable, high-quality translation services to individuals, businesses, and communities.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pripoli_text float_left mt-4">
                        <h5>Our Mission</h5>
                        <p>
                            Our mission is to empower aspiring translators by providing them with the practical opportunities they need to succeed in the job market. 
                            By connecting students directly with clients, we foster an environment of learning and growth that supports not only the students but also the community at large.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pripoli_text float_left mt-4">
                        <h5>What We Do</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>For Students:</strong> We provide aspiring and professional translators with opportunities to gain valuable experience, earn income, 
                            and enhance their translation skills through a wide variety of translation projects, ranging from legal to audiovisual translation.</li>

                            <li><strong>For Clients:</strong> We offer affordable, high-quality translation services in various fields, including written translation, audiovisual translation, 
                            oral interpretation, and more. Our platform ensures that clients receive culturally accurate and professionally vetted translations.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pripoli_text float_left mt-4">
                        <h5>Our Vision</h5>
                        <p>
                            We envision a world where language is no longer a barrier to communication and understanding. 
                            By cultivating the next generation of skilled translators, we aim to create a global platform where people from all walks of life can 
                            communicate seamlessly across languages and cultures.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pripoli_text float_left mt-4">
                        <h5>Our Partners</h5>
                        <p>
                            Translation Nation collaborates with leading academic and professional institutions, such as Applied Science Private University 
                            and the Jordanian Translators Association (JTA), to ensure the highest standards of education and translation quality are maintained on our platform.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pripoli_text float_left mt-4">
                        <h5>Join Us</h5>
                        <p>
                            Whether you're a student looking to gain experience or a business in need of reliable translation services, Translation Nation is here to help. 
                            Explore our services, connect with skilled translators, and become part of our global community today.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
